reviewer_info: Posted by Pakwheels User on Jul 14, 2021
review_text: One of the few EP82 GT Turbo starlet. Completely converted to Gt from exterior and interior. Engine setup is a 4efte which comes from factory in Gt. It is a turbine powered boosted engibe with a displacement of 1300cc. The car has all the necessary features of its time and it is a very good project with not a lot of money spent. It is very fast in its category. There are some other upgrades done to the engine which makes it even more special, unique and rare.
